description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Democrat Tim Ryan doubling down on his call to 'kill and confront' MAGA republicans, the FBI releasing its Uniform Crime Report that showed more people were killed in 2020 with fists & feet than were killed with rifles, and Tulsi Gabbards announcement that she will leave the Democratic party due to cowardly wokeness & anti-white racism.
